  title: "Words Per Minute Calculator - Free Online Tool",
  description: "Calculate your typing or reading speed in words per minute. Enter word count and time to get WPM, plus time estimates for common document lengths.",
  canonical: everyday_words_per_minute_url,
  og: {
    title: "Words Per Minute Calculator - Free Online Tool | Calc Hammer",
    description: "Measure typing or reading speed in WPM. Get time estimates for emails, blog posts, reports, and more.",
    url: everyday_words_per_minute_url,
    type: "website",
    site_name: "Calc Hammer"
  }
) %>

<%# JSON-LD schemas %>
<%= breadcrumb_schema([
  { name: "Home", url: root_url },
  { name: "Everyday", url: category_url("everyday") },
  { name: "Words Per Minute Calculator", url: everyday_words_per_minute_url }
]) %>

<%= faq_schema([
  { question: "How do I calculate words per minute?", answer: "Divide the total number of words by the time in minutes. For example, if you typed 450 words in 10 minutes, your speed is 450 / 10 = 45 WPM. For reading, count the words on a page or use a word counter, then divide by the time it took to read." },
  { question: "What is a good typing speed?", answer: "The average typing speed is 40 WPM for casual typists. Professional typists typically achieve 65-75 WPM. Administrative professionals average 50-80 WPM. Expert typists can exceed 100 WPM. For most jobs, 40-60 WPM is considered adequate, while 60+ WPM is considered fast." },
  { question: "What is the average reading speed?", answer: "The average adult reading speed is 200-250 words per minute for non-fiction and 250-300 WPM for fiction. College students average about 300 WPM. Speed readers can achieve 400-700 WPM, though comprehension may decrease at higher speeds. Technical material is typically read at 100-200 WPM." },
  { question: "How long does it take to read 1,000 words?", answer: "At the average reading speed of 238 WPM, it takes about 4.2 minutes to read 1,000 words. A fast reader at 350 WPM takes about 2.9 minutes. A slower reader at 150 WPM takes about 6.7 minutes. Content creators use this to estimate reading time for articles and blog posts." },
  { question: "How can I improve my typing speed?", answer: "Practice touch typing without looking at the keyboard. Use online typing tutors and games. Focus on accuracy first, then speed. Practice regularly for 15-30 minutes daily. Learn proper finger placement on the home row. Type actual content rather than random letters. Most people can improve from 30 to 60 WPM within a few weeks of consistent practice." }
]) %>

<%= calculator_schema_with_ratings(
  name: "Words Per Minute Calculator",
  description: "Calculate words per minute typing or reading speed with time estimates for common document lengths.",
  url: everyday_words_per_minute_url,
  category: "UtilityApplication",
  calculator_slug: "words-per-minute"
) %>

<%# Breadcrumbs %>
<%= render "shared/breadcrumbs", items: [
  { name: "Home", url: root_path },
  { name: "Everyday", url: category_path("everyday") },
  { name: "Words Per Minute Calculator" }
] %>

<div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-8">
  <div class="lg:col-span-2">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">Words Per Minute Calculator</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Measure your typing or reading speed and see how long common documents would take at your pace.</p>

    <%# Ad: leaderboard — placed below content heading per AdSense best practices %>
    <div class="mb-8"><%= render "shared/ad_slot", slot: "leaderboard" %></div>

    <div data-controller="words-per-minute-calculator ad-engagement" class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <label for="words-per-minute-word-count" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1.5">Word Count</label>
            <input id="words-per-minute-word-count" type="number" inputmode="decimal" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="wordCount" data-action="input->words-per-minute-calculator#calculate" class="w-full" placeholder="450" step="1" min="1">
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="words-per-minute-time" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1.5">Time (Minutes)</label>
            <input id="words-per-minute-time" type="number" inputmode="decimal" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="timeMinutes" data-action="input->words-per-minute-calculator#calculate" class="w-full" placeholder="10" step="1" min="0">
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="words-per-minute-time-2" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1.5">Time (Seconds)</label>
            <input id="words-per-minute-time-2" type="number" inputmode="decimal" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="timeSeconds" data-action="input->words-per-minute-calculator#calculate" class="w-full" value="0" step="1" min="0" max="59">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true" class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-indigo-900/20 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-5">Results</h2>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Words Per Minute</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="resultWpm">--</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Characters/Min</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="resultCpm">--</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Total Time</span>
              <span class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="resultTotalMinutes">--</span>
            </div>
            <hr class="border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Time Estimates at Your Speed</p>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Email (200 words)</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="resultEmailTime">--</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Novel Page (250 words)</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="resultNovelPageTime">--</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Blog Post (1,500 words)</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="resultBlogTime">--</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Essay (2,000 words)</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="resultEssayTime">--</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Report (3,000 words)</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="resultReportTime">--</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Thesis (20,000 words)</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" data-words-per-minute-calculator-target="resultThesisTime">--</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button data-action="click->words-per-minute-calculator#copy" class="mt-6 w-full px-4 py-2.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-indigo-700 text-white rounded-xl shadow-sm shadow-blue-500/20 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-blue-500/25 transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 text-sm font-medium">Copy Results</button>
        </div>
